ue to an accidental overdose of fentanyl. He earned $120 million in 2021. John Lennon was a famous British musician, songwriter and peace activist who died of gunshot wounds back in December 1980 after he was shot four times by a fan. It has been years since he died and he is still making money. He earned $12 million in 2021.